To introduce your client’s company name on Facebook, run a Brand Awareness or Reach campaign in Meta Platforms Facebook Ads Manager.

Here’s the simple process:

Choose Campaign Objective
Brand Awareness → Show ads to people likely to remember the brand.
Reach → Show ads to as many people as possible.

Create Eye-Catching Creative
Use:

Company logo
Business name
Short slogan
Attractive image/video

Example text:
“Welcome to ABC Company – Your Trusted Web Development Partner!”

Target Right Audience
Select:

Location (country/city)
Age & gender
Interests related to the business

Example:
If company provides web services:
Target people interested in:

Web design
eCommerce
Digital marketing
Set Budget
Start with small budget:
$5–$10/day for testing
Choose Placement
Automatic placement is best:
Facebook Feed
Instagram Feed
Stories
Reels
Add CTA button
Such as:
Learn More
Contact Us
Send Message

Best ad types for company introduction:

Image Ad → Simple logo + offer
Video Ad → Short company intro video
Carousel Ad → Show multiple services/products

Example ad copy:

Headline:
“Welcome to ABC Company”

Primary Text:
“We provide professional web design, development, and digital marketing services. Contact us today!”

This type of ad helps increase:
✅ Brand awareness
✅ Page likes/follows
✅ Website visits
✅ Messages/leads later
